These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, lemonade, water, cola, mirinda, hot-chocolate
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, brazilian, thai, indonesian, american, japanese, canadian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, skiing, rugby, biathlon, soccer, rowing, parkour
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, airplane, boat, scooter, taxi, trike, car
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is soccer is the indonesian##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the brazilian is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the colombian is on the right of the canadian##1
 6. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the american##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the car and the japanese##2
 9. the american is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking cola##1
12. the person drinking cola is the person driving the roller##1
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the thai##1
14. the japanese is the person driving the boat##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the canadian##1
16. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
17. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the thai##1
18. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the american##1
19. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | milk  | mirinda        | cola | lemonade      | water     | iced-tea      | hot-chocolate     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian         | canadian   | colombian | japanese    | american | thai |
| Sport         | rugby | soccer | water-polo | skiing | parkour  | rowing  | biathlon    |
| Transport     | taxi  | trike         | roller     | airplane    | boat | scooter     | car     |

